property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
WITH "CTE_Agg_CustDocClearing" AS (
    SELECT 
        "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID"                                                 AS "ID",
        "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Time"                                                        AS "Time",
        "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ChangedBy"                                                   AS "ExecutedBy",
        "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ExecutionType"                                               AS "ExecutionType",
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID"     
            ORDER BY "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Time" ASC)                                      AS "rn"
    FROM "o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem"
        LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem_Changes"
            ON "ReceivableItem"."ID" = "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ObjectID"            
    WHERE "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Attribute" IN ('Clearing','Clearing-NonReceipts')
        AND "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL 
        AND "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID"  IS NOT NULL 
)
SELECT  
    'ClearReceivableItem' || '::' || "Agg_CustDocClearing"."ID"                         AS "ID",
    "Agg_CustDocClearing"."Time"                                                        AS "Time",
    "Agg_CustDocClearing"."ExecutedBy"                                                  AS "ExecutedBy",
    "Agg_CustDocClearing"."ExecutionType"                                               AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "CTE_Agg_CustDocClearing" AS "Agg_CustDocClearing"      
WHERE "Agg_CustDocClearing"."rn" = 1

SELECT 
    'ClearReceivableItem' || '::' || "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID"                AS "ID",
    "ReceivableItem"."ID"                                                                  AS "ReceivableItem"
FROM "o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem_Changes"
        ON "ReceivableItem"."ID" = "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ObjectID"
WHERE "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Attribute" IN ('Clearing','Clearing-NonReceipts')
    AND "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID"  IS NOT NULL
